      <title>霍尔兹曼告诉普拉托，欧洲央行不应在六月和七月都降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/ecb-shouldn-t-cut-in-both-june-and-july-holzmann-tells-platow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员罗伯特·霍尔兹曼在接受 Platow Brief 采访时表示，欧洲央行不应在 6 月和 7 月连续降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/ecb-shouldn-t-cut-in-both-june-and-july-holzmann-tells-platow</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
