    <item>
      <title>北京进一步放松非核心区域购房限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/beijing-further-loosens-home-buying-curbs-in-non-core-areas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国首都北京将允许家庭在非核心地区再购买一套住房，因为即使是中国最大的城市也面临着创纪录的房地产低迷的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/beijing-further-loosens-home-buying-curbs-in-non-core-areas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 12:58:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德莱纳姆：美联储降息“健康延迟”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/fed-in-a-healthy-delay-on-rate-cuts-blackrock-s-lynam-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德(BlackRock)宏观信贷研究主管阿曼达·莱纳姆(Amanda Lynam)在讨论美联储推迟降息时表示，“我们需要的是宏观政策的明确性，但不一定是在降息方面有利的宏观政策”。莱纳姆还研究了信贷发行所显示的企业应对更高利率的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/fed-in-a-healthy-delay-on-rate-cuts-blackrock-s-lynam-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 12:48:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万科退出非核心业务，剥离资产流动性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/vanke-to-exit-non-core-business-divest-assets-for-liquidity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周二股东大会的一份备忘录，万科公司将退出非核心业务并剥离资产，因为该开发商寻求在该行业前所未有的低迷时期增加流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/vanke-to-exit-non-core-business-divest-assets-for-liquidity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 12:40:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
